            "locale": "en",
            "hint": "After negative/restrictive adverbials (Never, Hardly, Not only, Seldom, Only then…), **subject-auxiliary inversion** is required.\nThe inverted auxiliary must match the tense of the original clause. Only the auxiliary comes before the subject.",
